  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2).",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/cpb-hemolysis-mrl2-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cpb-hemolysis-worst-case-claim-001",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/cfd-hemolysis-centrifugal-pump-001",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-generic-cpb-experimental-dataset-001",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/cpb-operating-conditions-dataset-002"
  ],
  "hasValidationResult": [
