    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scoping for a Class II CPB device. The credibility evidence package is accepted as sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
